    <!-- Introduction Arrays -->
    <!-- Text Items-->
    <string-array name="introduction_texts">
        <item>Hello there! Glad to meet you!
            Welcome to the world of Stepventure!
            My name is Brobot! People call me the Stepventure Prof!
        </item>

        <item>This world is inhabited by creatures called Stepmon!
            For some people, Stepmon are pets. Others use them for fights. Myselfâ€¦ I study Stepmon as
            a profession.
        </item>

        <item>On the dashboard screen you can track how many steps you have taken into the world of Stepventure.
            It\'s also a place where you can start and pause your adventure.
        </item>

        <item>Simply click on the Start Adventure button to start your adventure!
            Take steps in the real world and wait till you get attacked by a Stepmon.</item>

        <item>While the Adventuremode is active, the Stepventure notification will keep you informed.
            Stopping the Adventuremode will remove the notification.</item>

        <item>On the statistics screen you can check your current statistics, such as your level, attack damage, defense and how much experience you need till the next level!
        </item>

        <item>When you encounter a Stepmon you can choose to fight!
            Attack with your sword, bash with your shield and eventually shoot lasers to ensure victory.
        </item>

        <item>Your very own Stepventure legend is about to unfold!
            A world of dreams and adventures with Stepmon awaits! Let\'s go!
        </item>
    </string-array>
